entries.arrival_phase_1: Scanning system for target. Stand by to proceed with the attack.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Nav location to the target has been located. Proceed with extreme prejudice.
entries.assassinate_success: Good work, pilot. Now lets find out what they want.
entries.destroy_escort: The entire squad must be eradicated.
entries.failed_escape: Aklee Skorba escaped! How could you let that happen!!
entries.quest_escort_d: Make sure none of them escapes.
entries.quest_location_d: The ships are still in Ord Mantell space.
entries.quest_location_t: Ord Mantell System - Nova Orion Sector.
entries.quest_target_d: Take out the strange ships. Find out who or what Vaine is.
entries.split_quest_alert: We detected a transmission to one of the ships from the Tatooine System. Seems some of your attackers must have gone there after their initial assault.
entries.title: Nova Orion: Destroy the Mysterious ships
entries.title_d: These ships attacked you, but fled once you had the upper hand. Finish them this time.
